User Stories - Books

 as a user I want to have the ability to login/register so that I may use the participate in group involvement 

 as a user I want to set a profile up so that I may customize my experience

 as a user I want to have to ability log my books for further record

 as a a user I want to rate my book so that I can share my enjoyment 

 as a user want to make comments on books I’ve read for viewing 

 as a user want to see books that other users/“friends” have read 

 as a user want to comment/communicate with other users to share experiences/ recommendations 

as a user I want to show my progress of completion so that I may compare my progress with other users
